text_description: {pitcher} SPIKES ONE IN THE DIRT, BUT WITH NO RUNNERS, NO DAMAGE DONE.
WILD PITCH! {pitcher} LOSES HIS GRIP, BUT NOBODY IS ON BASE.
{pitcher} THROWS ONE TO THE BACKSTOP, BUT NO RUNNERS TO ADVANCE.
THAT ONE GOT AWAY FROM {pitcher}, BUT NO ONE TO TAKE ADVANTAGE.
A WILD ONE FROM {pitcher}, BUT NO BASE RUNNERS MEANS NO HARM.
{pitcher} LOSES CONTROL! THE CATCHER BLOCKS IT, BUT THERE'S NO THREAT.
BALL SKIPS PAST THE CATCHER, BUT NO RUNNERS MEANS NO CONSEQUENCES.
A WILD PITCH FROM {pitcher}! LUCKILY, THE BASES ARE EMPTY.
THAT FASTBALL SLIPPED! {pitcher} FIRES ONE TO THE BACKSTOP.
{pitcher} UNLEASHES ONE TO THE BACK WALL—THANKFULLY, NO RUNNERS ON.
WILD PITCH! {batter} WATCHES AS THE RUNNER TAKES SECOND BASE!
THAT ONE GOT AWAY FROM {pitcher}! THE RUNNER ADVANCES TO SECOND.
{pitcher} SPIKES IT IN THE DIRT! THE RUNNER MOVES UP!
BALL IN THE DIRT! NO CHANCE FOR THE CATCHER—THE RUNNER TAKES SECOND.
WILD PITCH FROM {pitcher}! THE RUNNER MOVES INTO SCORING POSITION!
A COSTLY MISTAKE FROM {pitcher}—THE RUNNER TAKES SECOND EASILY.
THAT BALL GETS PAST THE CATCHER! RUNNER MOVES UP TO SECOND!
TOO FAR INSIDE! {pitcher} LOSES CONTROL, RUNNER TAKES SECOND BASE.
A BOUNCER TO THE BACKSTOP! RUNNER ADVANCES ON THE WILD PITCH!
{batter} SEES THE RUNNER MOVE AS {pitcher} LOSES CONTROL!
WILD PITCH! THE RUNNER DASHES TO THIRD BASE!
MISSED LOCATION! {pitcher} LOSES IT, AND THE RUNNER TAKES THIRD!
{batter} WATCHES AS A WILD PITCH LETS THE RUNNER ADVANCE TO THIRD!
THAT ONE SKIPS AWAY! THE RUNNER TAKES THIRD BASE EASILY.
{pitcher} SPIKES ONE—NO CHANCE FOR THE CATCHER, RUNNER TO THIRD!
BIG OPPORTUNITY NOW! WILD PITCH MOVES THE RUNNER TO THIRD.
BACKSTOP BOUNCE! {pitcher} PAYS FOR HIS MISTAKE, RUNNER ON THIRD.
TOO FAR INSIDE! THE RUNNER HUSTLES AND TAKES THIRD BASE!
{batter} HOLDS BACK AS {pitcher} LOSES CONTROL—RUNNER MOVES UP!
A SLIDER IN THE DIRT GETS AWAY! RUNNER NOW JUST 90 FEET AWAY.
WILD PITCH! THE RUNNER SPRINTS HOME AND SCORES!
THAT ONE GETS AWAY—AND THE RUNNER COMES IN TO SCORE!
COSTLY MISTAKE! {pitcher} UNLEASHES A WILD PITCH, AND A RUN SCORES!
THE CROWD REACTS AS THE RUNNER TAKES OFF—SAFE AT HOME!
A BRUTAL BREAK FOR {pitcher}! WILD PITCH BRINGS IN A RUN!
{pitcher} SPIKES IT—NO CHANCE FOR THE CATCHER, AND THE RUN SCORES!
{batter} WATCHES AS A RUN SCORES ON A WILD PITCH!
TOO FAR INSIDE—AND THE RUNNER TAKES HOME PLATE!
NO CHANCE TO STOP THAT ONE! THE RUNNER SCORES ON A WILD PITCH!
FREE RUN! {pitcher} LOSES CONTROL, AND THE RUNNER SCORES!
WILD PITCH! BOTH RUNNERS ADVANCE—NOW SECOND AND THIRD!
A COSTLY SLIP FROM {pitcher}! THE RUNNERS MOVE INTO SCORING POSITION!
THAT BALL GETS AWAY! RUNNERS MOVE UP TO SECOND AND THIRD!
MISSED LOCATION! THE CATCHER CAN'T STOP IT, RUNNERS ADVANCE!
TOO FAR OUTSIDE! BOTH RUNNERS TAKE AN EXTRA BASE!
BAD PITCH FROM {pitcher}! DOUBLE ADVANCEMENT ON THE BASE PATHS!
THE CATCHER CHASES IT, BUT TOO LATE—BOTH RUNNERS ADVANCE!
{pitcher} CAN'T FIND THE ZONE! WILD PITCH MOVES UP BOTH RUNNERS!
BIG MISTAKE! {pitcher} LOSES CONTROL, AND THE RUNNERS MOVE UP!
A BRUTAL SLIP! {batter} SEES BOTH RUNNERS ADVANCE!
WILD PITCH! RUNNER FROM THIRD SCORES, AND THE TRAIL RUNNER MOVES UP!
{pitcher} LOSES IT! RUN COMES HOME, AND NOW A RUNNER ON SECOND!
TOO FAR INSIDE! THE RUNNER TAKES HOME, AND ANOTHER ONE ADVANCES!
A RUN SCORES ON THE WILD PITCH! THE OTHER RUNNER MOVES UP!
THAT ONE GOT AWAY BADLY! A RUNNER SCORES, AND THE OTHER TAKES SECOND!
THE THROW BACK IS TOO LATE! A RUN SCORES ON THE WILD PITCH!
{pitcher} SPIKES ONE, AND THE RUNNER FROM THIRD TAKES HOME!
THE RUNNER FROM THIRD SCORES, AND THE OTHER MOVES INTO SCORING POSITION!
WILD PITCH! ONE RUN SCORES, ANOTHER RUNNER MOVES UP!
THE BASE PATHS SHIFT AS {pitcher} LOSES CONTROL!
WILD PITCH! THE RUNNER FROM THIRD SCORES, AND THE OTHER MOVES TO THIRD!
{pitcher} SPIKES IT—ONE RUN IN, AND A RUNNER ON THIRD!
THE CATCHER CAN'T BLOCK IT! A RUN SCORES, AND A RUNNER MOVES UP!
MISSED LOCATION! RUN COMES IN, AND NOW THE OTHER RUNNER STANDS ON THIRD!
TOO FAR INSIDE! RUN SCORES, AND ANOTHER 90 FEET CLOSER!
{pitcher} THROWS IT AWAY! A RUN SCORES, AND A RUNNER REMAINS ON THIRD!
BAD PITCH FROM {pitcher}! A RUN SCORES EASILY, AND THE TRAILING RUNNER MOVES UP!
THE CATCHER CHASES IT, BUT THE DAMAGE IS DONE—ONE RUN IN, ANOTHER ON THIRD!
BIG MISTAKE! {pitcher} LOSES CONTROL, AND THE SCORE CHANGES!
A BRUTAL SLIP! {batter} WATCHES AS A RUN SCORES!
WILD PITCH! A RUN SCORES, AND THE OTHER RUNNERS ADVANCE!
COSTLY ERROR! {pitcher} LOSES CONTROL—RUNNERS MOVE UP, ONE SCORES!
THAT ONE GOT AWAY BADLY! A RUN SCORES, AND THE BASES SHIFT!
{pitcher} SPIKES IT! A RUN SCORES, AND TWO MORE MOVE INTO POSITION!
THE THROW BACK IS TOO LATE! A RUN SCORES ON THE WILD PITCH!
BAD PITCH FROM {pitcher}! ONE RUN IN, AND THE BASES STILL LOADED!
THE CATCHER CAN'T BLOCK IT! A RUN SCORES, AND THE OTHERS MOVE UP!
MISSED LOCATION! RUN COMES IN, AND NOW TWO MORE IN SCORING POSITION!
TOO FAR INSIDE! A RUN SCORES, AND THE PRESSURE BUILDS!
A FREE RUN! {pitcher} LOSES CONTROL, AND EVERYONE MOVES!
